init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the “Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The drug is recalled, and the government is forced to pay for the cost of the drug and the side effects.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are one of the few people who are not affected by the drug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have decided to take action.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You want to save humanity from itself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You want to stop this drug from ever being used again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have decided to create a new drug that will counteract the effects of the immortality drug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: decide to test it out on yourself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: is now living a normal life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are hailed as the savior of humanity.
